## Future enhancements (parked)

- **Org-level admin accounts** so each program director only sees results for
  staff in their own center
- **Direct SSO from the MSA Platform** so mentors and mentees don't need to
  re-enter their name and email when launching the quiz from their dashboard
- **Embedded link-to-results** in the MSA Platform so mentors and mentees can
  see their LEAP profile alongside their reflections without switching apps
